Here's a short PHP code demonstrating Process Control:

    <?php 
    $pid = pcntl_fork();
    if ($pid == -1) {
         die('could not fork');
    } else if ($pid) {
         // we are the parent
         pcntl_wait($status); // Protect against Zombie children
